                     <interp inst="t18280110-114-person761" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am apprentice to Mr. Barker, a pawnbroker. I produce this petticoat, which was pawned by the prisoner, on the 4th of January.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280110-114-person762">
                  WILLIAM 
                  DODD
               <interp inst="t18280110-114-person762" type="surname" value="DODD"></interp>
