                     <interp inst="t18280110-114-person762" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a patrol. The prisoner was brought to Bow-street, on Saturday, the 5th - I found three duplicates on her - one for the petticoat, and another for the cap - these gloves and purse were found on her - she gave no account of them.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I beg for mercy.</p>
